WEBVTT

01:45.079 --> 01:45.640
So that's how it is.

01:45.640 --> 01:47.239
It's because of our sunlight situation.

01:47.359 --> 01:48.599
So for this whole project,

01:49.079 --> 01:50.599
we had to give up some green space.

01:50.799 --> 01:51.239
See?

01:51.719 --> 01:52.959
Actually, you just mentioned

02:02.200 --> 02:02.840
Turn off the air conditioner.

02:03.079 --> 02:03.319
Okay.

02:14.919 --> 02:15.599
So,

02:19.439 --> 02:20.520
we can now

02:20.599 --> 02:21.879
keep moving this forward

02:22.280 --> 02:23.280
and push ahead with it.

02:24.400 --> 02:24.879
Alright.

02:27.039 --> 02:27.599
And then,

02:27.599 --> 02:28.400
let's discuss

02:28.400 --> 02:29.319
another proposal.

02:29.680 --> 02:30.319
That is,

02:31.039 --> 02:31.719
we

02:49.520 --> 02:50.080
That's excellent.

02:50.560 --> 02:51.120
So if

02:51.120 --> 02:52.080
there are no issues,

02:52.159 --> 02:53.199
let's adjourn, shall we?

02:54.360 --> 02:54.840
Meeting adjourned.

02:55.000 --> 02:55.520
Thank you all for your hard work.

02:56.199 --> 02:56.719
Okay.

03:08.759 --> 03:09.280
Ms. Xu

03:14.080 --> 03:14.759
Ms. Xu

03:23.240 --> 03:23.840
Mr. Shen

03:24.599 --> 03:25.159
Sorry about that.

03:25.400 --> 03:26.120
Sorry to keep you waiting.

03:26.840 --> 03:27.719
Let's have lunch together.

03:27.919 --> 03:28.560
We can talk while we eat.

03:39.680 --> 03:40.199
Ms. Xu

03:59.599 --> 04:00.039
Nurse

04:00.759 --> 04:01.520
Please be gentle.

04:12.560 --> 04:13.960
Family, please watch the patient closely.

04:14.000 --> 04:14.719
Call me if you need anything.

04:15.439 --> 04:15.800
Okay.

04:16.120 --> 04:16.519
Thank you.

05:01.160 --> 05:01.639
You're awake.

05:09.879 --> 05:10.279
Come on.

05:14.399 --> 05:15.720
You had a fever at my office

05:16.120 --> 05:16.759
and fainted.

05:17.160 --> 05:18.319
I brought you here.

05:21.800 --> 05:23.040
Thank you, Mr. Shen.

05:23.600 --> 05:24.279
You're welcome.

05:24.800 --> 05:26.480
I was a bit careless this time.

05:27.040 --> 05:27.959
I thought taking a couple pills

05:28.000 --> 05:28.759
would get me through it.

05:30.040 --> 05:30.759
The doctor said

05:31.160 --> 05:32.000
you're overworked

05:32.519 --> 05:33.639
and need to rest.

05:38.279 --> 05:38.759
Sorry.

05:44.519 --> 05:45.199
Mr. Shen,

05:46.319 --> 05:47.279
you can go ahead with your work.

05:47.519 --> 05:48.680
I can take care of myself.

05:48.920 --> 05:49.480
Thank you.

05:52.720 --> 05:54.040
I'm the one who called you out.

05:54.560 --> 05:55.800
So I have to take responsibility.

05:56.480 --> 05:57.360
Once your fever's gone,

05:57.839 --> 05:59.040
I still owe you an interview.

06:03.800 --> 06:04.079
By the way,

06:04.639 --> 06:05.399
the doctor said

06:07.199 --> 06:07.920
you should drink more water.

06:09.279 --> 06:09.639
Here.

06:13.639 --> 06:14.160
Thank you.

06:17.800 --> 06:19.240
After the nurse removed the needle,

06:19.600 --> 06:20.560
I was worried you'd keep bleeding,

06:21.000 --> 06:22.120
so I put a bandage on for you.

07:02.519 --> 07:03.519
Hao Ming is back.

07:05.079 --> 07:05.920
Take it over there to play.

07:06.720 --> 07:07.040
Mom.

07:07.600 --> 07:08.879
Let me formally introduce you.

07:09.439 --> 07:10.319
This is Xu Yan.

07:10.439 --> 07:11.160
She's my girlfriend.

07:12.079 --> 07:12.800
Hello, Auntie Yu.

07:12.879 --> 07:13.680
I'm Xu Yan.

07:17.480 --> 07:18.560
This is Auntie Ma.

07:19.360 --> 07:19.959
And this is Auntie Meng.

07:20.720 --> 07:21.879
It's nice to meet you all.

07:22.040 --> 07:22.959
Auntie Ma, Auntie Meng,

07:24.279 --> 07:25.639
Hao Ming always talks about you.

07:25.839 --> 07:27.120
It's great to finally meet.

07:27.519 --> 07:28.360
Welcome.

07:29.839 --> 07:30.279
Please, have a seat.

07:33.600 --> 07:34.160
Thank you.

07:36.680 --> 07:37.199
Hao Ming,

07:37.519 --> 07:38.680
Dad is waiting for you in the study.

07:38.800 --> 07:39.839
He said he wants to talk to you.

07:40.399 --> 07:40.720
Okay.

07:41.959 --> 07:42.839
Take good care of Yan Yan for me.

07:43.319 --> 07:44.240
Got it, don't worry.

07:47.399 --> 07:48.199
Have some water.

07:49.120 --> 07:49.839
Auntie, I can do it myself.

07:49.959 --> 07:50.600
Let me pour you some more.

07:51.000 --> 07:51.399
Thank you.

07:53.759 --> 07:54.519
I'll add a little for you.

07:58.480 --> 08:00.560
Your Xiaobu is really smart.

08:00.800 --> 08:02.120
No wonder it won at the World Canine Union

08:02.160 --> 08:03.560
dog show.

08:17.720 --> 08:19.680
I'm really sorry.

08:19.839 --> 08:20.879
I'm late.

08:21.120 --> 08:22.439
I took Pudding for grooming.

08:22.680 --> 08:23.439
Yes.

08:24.279 --> 08:24.920
Take it to play.

08:27.000 --> 08:27.800
This is

08:28.680 --> 08:29.680
Let me introduce you.

08:29.920 --> 08:30.759
She's Xu Yan.

08:30.959 --> 08:31.759
Hao Ming's friend.

08:33.559 --> 08:34.440
Hello, Xiao Xu.

08:34.639 --> 08:35.480
I'm Sun Meiling.

08:35.559 --> 08:36.600
I'm Lan's friend.

08:38.159 --> 08:39.000
Hello, Ms. Sun.

08:39.279 --> 08:40.000
I'm Xu Yan.

08:43.120 --> 08:43.679
Ms. Sun,

08:43.919 --> 08:44.360
Please, have a seat.

08:45.159 --> 08:46.159
Thank you, Xiao Xu.

08:53.720 --> 08:54.320
Xiao Xu,

08:54.960 --> 08:55.840
Do you like dogs?

08:58.279 --> 08:59.320
I really like dogs.

09:00.480 --> 09:02.440
Do you have a dog now?

09:03.759 --> 09:05.039
I'm too busy with work,

09:05.120 --> 09:06.519
so I haven't had time to get one.

09:07.039 --> 09:08.279
I'm afraid I can't take good care of them.

09:10.960 --> 09:11.600
It's barking.

09:12.559 --> 09:13.200
Come here.

09:15.360 --> 09:15.960
Xiaobu.

09:17.600 --> 09:18.559
Our Pudding at home

09:18.799 --> 09:19.799
is just a silly dog.

09:20.159 --> 09:21.120
Other than being cute,

09:21.440 --> 09:22.240
it's not much else.

09:25.960 --> 09:26.360
It's alright.

09:26.360 --> 09:28.279
No, it's pretty smart.

09:28.399 --> 09:29.120
Pudding is great.

09:29.200 --> 09:29.759
Come on.

09:30.080 --> 09:31.159
Do you want to go down too?

09:31.720 --> 09:32.279
Xiao Hui,

09:33.080 --> 09:35.240
Bring some fruit and a fresh pot of tea.

09:47.919 --> 09:48.559
Let me help you carry it.

09:49.679 --> 09:50.000
Okay.

09:50.200 --> 09:50.759
Thank you.

09:51.399 --> 09:52.320
Auntie Yu, I'll see you out.

09:53.159 --> 09:53.480
Alright.

09:59.600 --> 10:00.879
Let me braid your hair.

10:13.600 --> 10:14.399
Ms. Xu,

10:16.480 --> 10:17.279
I think

10:18.320 --> 10:19.200
among all the ladies here,

10:19.240 --> 10:21.039
the ones coming and going,

10:21.879 --> 10:22.519
you're different.

10:26.399 --> 10:27.320
How am I different?

10:38.080 --> 10:40.399
Your hair is a bit dry and frizzy.

10:42.919 --> 10:43.440
Lan and the others

10:43.440 --> 10:45.120
really care about their hair.

10:52.320 --> 10:54.320
I'm usually too busy with work.

10:54.600 --> 10:55.559
So I don't have time.

10:57.240 --> 10:57.960
They

10:58.200 --> 10:59.399
often go for a kind of

10:59.399 --> 11:00.440
hair treatment.

11:00.919 --> 11:01.679
After it's done,

11:01.759 --> 11:03.320
their hair shines like satin.

11:03.399 --> 11:04.240
It's really popular.

11:05.279 --> 11:06.480
Ms. Ma and Ms. Sun

11:06.519 --> 11:07.480
also go there often.

11:08.000 --> 11:09.000
You should try it too.

11:09.399 --> 11:09.960
Xiao Hui

11:11.720 --> 11:12.440
Lan

11:13.080 --> 11:13.840
Is the tea ready?

11:14.720 --> 11:15.600
It's ready.

11:24.279 --> 11:25.440
Just let them handle it.

11:27.799 --> 11:28.279
Thank you.

11:28.919 --> 11:29.399
You're welcome.

11:32.559 --> 11:33.200
Xu Yan

11:34.200 --> 11:35.399
Stay for dinner with us.

11:37.600 --> 11:38.080
Okay.

11:39.320 --> 11:40.799
I ordered a few dishes at the club.

11:41.559 --> 11:42.320
Once they're ready,

11:42.320 --> 11:43.120
go pick them up.

11:43.480 --> 11:44.159
Go out and turn right.

11:44.480 --> 11:45.279
You'll find it.

11:49.080 --> 11:50.279
If it's the club,

11:50.320 --> 11:51.679
can't they deliver it here?

11:52.679 --> 11:53.360
I don't really like

11:53.360 --> 11:54.480
strangers coming to my home.

12:00.320 --> 12:00.840
Alright.

12:03.919 --> 12:05.159
I'll go get it now.

12:12.399 --> 12:12.960
Xu Yan

12:15.320 --> 12:16.240
There are a lot of people today.

12:16.480 --> 12:18.039
So I can't really chat with you.

12:19.600 --> 12:20.200
Later,

12:20.200 --> 12:21.200
after you pick up the food,

12:21.240 --> 12:22.120
just give it to Auntie.

12:22.320 --> 12:23.120
You can head home first.

12:24.159 --> 12:25.080
I'll let Hao Ming know.

12:35.919 --> 12:36.399
Okay.

12:38.320 --> 12:39.759
Are you free Saturday morning?

12:41.480 --> 12:41.919
Yes.

12:42.480 --> 12:42.799
Alright.

12:43.200 --> 12:44.039
I'll pick the place.

12:45.279 --> 12:45.720
Let's talk.

13:18.639 --> 13:19.159
Come in.

13:21.279 --> 13:21.759
Director.

13:22.000 --> 13:23.360
The proposal for the next episode

13:23.399 --> 13:24.120
is here for you.

13:26.399 --> 13:26.879
Xu Yan

13:27.639 --> 13:28.320
Have a seat first.

13:35.080 --> 13:35.360
Sit.

13:36.279 --> 13:36.840
Xu Yan,

13:37.080 --> 13:38.200
during your interview,

13:38.720 --> 13:40.159
I spotted your potential right away.

13:41.320 --> 13:42.799
Since you joined us,

13:43.039 --> 13:44.799
I've put a lot of effort into mentoring you.

13:45.879 --> 13:47.519
I have high hopes for you.

13:48.080 --> 13:48.320
Come.

13:50.000 --> 13:50.879
I know, Director.

13:50.879 --> 13:51.480
That's why I've always

13:51.519 --> 13:52.440
been very grateful to you.

13:53.559 --> 13:54.440
No need to thank me.

13:55.720 --> 13:56.320
Xu Yan,

13:57.600 --> 13:58.519
all these years,

13:59.080 --> 14:00.600
this food show has been a hit.

14:01.480 --> 14:02.799
I had you plan

14:02.879 --> 14:04.000
Family Feast

14:04.799 --> 14:06.279
to help you build your credentials.

14:07.120 --> 14:08.039
So you could move up.

14:08.840 --> 14:10.200
And become a host later.

14:11.879 --> 14:12.360
You see,

14:12.480 --> 14:14.039
you have a good appearance,

14:14.679 --> 14:15.559
you're smart,

14:15.720 --> 14:16.480
and hardworking.

14:20.159 --> 14:21.120
But sometimes,

14:22.639 --> 14:23.759
things don't go as planned.

14:25.519 --> 14:26.759
Your application to be a host

14:27.000 --> 14:27.799
was rejected.

14:29.600 --> 14:30.120
Why?

14:32.399 --> 14:33.080
Why what?

14:34.240 --> 14:35.159
Because I remember

14:35.159 --> 14:36.279
last time you told me

14:36.399 --> 14:36.679
Xu Yan,

14:37.120 --> 14:37.639
sit down first.

14:38.759 --> 14:39.840
Just sit down.

14:43.960 --> 14:44.559
Director Zhou,

14:46.200 --> 14:47.799
when I first came here,

14:48.360 --> 14:49.960
I applied to be a host.

14:50.200 --> 14:50.559
Yes, yes.

14:50.600 --> 14:51.120
Isn't that right?

14:51.159 --> 14:51.600
Yes.

14:51.960 --> 14:53.759
You said I lacked experience.

14:53.840 --> 14:54.759
That I needed to gain some.

14:56.120 --> 14:57.440
So I worked as a planner.

14:57.639 --> 14:58.279
For three years.

14:58.720 --> 14:59.480
Yes, yes.

15:04.000 --> 15:05.519
When I started Family Feast,

15:05.679 --> 15:06.279
the proposal

15:06.279 --> 15:07.559
only had two big words.

15:09.320 --> 15:09.919
Start project.

15:10.240 --> 15:11.000
Invite guests.

15:11.679 --> 15:12.159
Interview.

15:12.559 --> 15:13.519
Filming, post-production.

15:13.759 --> 15:14.159
Subtitles.

15:14.240 --> 15:14.799
Each one

15:14.799 --> 15:15.960
I checked myself.

15:17.559 --> 15:18.120
I know

15:18.240 --> 15:19.720
a show can't just be theory.

15:19.759 --> 15:21.279
So I paid to learn cooking.

15:21.960 --> 15:23.039
I wanted to bring

15:23.080 --> 15:24.519
better ingredients to the show.

15:24.960 --> 15:26.279
I used my own salary.

15:26.799 --> 15:28.480
Family Feast has been three years now.

15:29.200 --> 15:30.360
Countless overtime,

15:31.399 --> 15:32.120
late nights made it happen.

15:33.879 --> 15:34.799
So I want to know

15:37.039 --> 15:37.519
why.

15:39.440 --> 15:40.000
Xu Yan,

15:41.440 --> 15:42.279
You're not convinced.

15:43.039 --> 15:43.759
I understand.

15:44.840 --> 15:46.360
You worked hard, you gave a lot.

15:46.759 --> 15:47.639
I know that too.

15:48.519 --> 15:50.519
But management has its own concerns.

15:51.080 --> 15:52.279
Don't get stuck on this.

15:52.320 --> 15:53.440
I'm not stuck.

15:55.360 --> 15:56.320
Where am I lacking?

15:56.919 --> 15:57.720
I can learn.

15:59.240 --> 15:59.960
Let me be direct.

16:00.799 --> 16:01.720
Our program center

16:02.080 --> 16:04.159
is pushing for media integration.

16:04.799 --> 16:06.720
Staff quotas for departments

16:06.919 --> 16:07.720
and production budgets

16:07.840 --> 16:08.919
are being cut sharply.

16:09.639 --> 16:10.559
At this critical moment,

16:10.759 --> 16:12.039
host positions

16:12.279 --> 16:14.440
require many factors to be considered.

16:15.679 --> 16:16.759
I fought for you.

16:17.440 --> 16:18.399
If Sun Siwei

16:18.440 --> 16:19.600
can't make it for any reason,

16:19.919 --> 16:20.799
you'll step in.

16:25.799 --> 16:26.759
Three years, Director

16:30.480 --> 16:31.080
Replaced by someone

16:31.080 --> 16:32.919
who could be let go at any time

16:34.440 --> 16:35.080
Don't say that

16:36.120 --> 16:36.519
Xu Yan

16:38.000 --> 16:39.360
I know you're upset

16:40.279 --> 16:42.120
But Sun Siwei does a great job too

16:42.639 --> 16:43.879
The management has already decided

16:44.000 --> 16:45.919
Sun Siwei will continue as host

16:46.679 --> 16:48.159
This isn't just my decision

16:48.320 --> 16:49.480
When the time is right

16:50.080 --> 16:51.759
you can get back to the starting line

16:52.080 --> 16:52.679
and it'll be fine

16:54.639 --> 16:56.559
Only by staying at the starting line

16:58.679 --> 16:59.879
do you earn the right to start

17:03.120 --> 17:03.480
Xu Yan

17:25.519 --> 17:26.359
Hello, Auntie Yu

17:27.079 --> 17:28.440
The place and time for dinner

17:28.759 --> 17:29.839
I've sent to your phone

17:30.240 --> 17:30.640
Okay

17:40.599 --> 17:40.920
Ma'am

17:41.200 --> 17:41.920
This is what you asked for

17:41.920 --> 17:42.640
hair care treatment

17:42.920 --> 17:43.960
But there's no discount

17:44.160 --> 17:44.799
Is that alright with you

17:49.279 --> 17:49.519
Alright

17:49.880 --> 17:50.319
Please wait a moment

17:50.440 --> 17:51.000
I'll get it ready now

17:52.599 --> 17:53.319
That lady just now

17:53.400 --> 17:54.519
wants the full treatment

17:54.759 --> 17:55.960
So we need to prepare

17:56.240 --> 17:57.079
Go get the supplies ready

18:14.039 --> 18:14.759
Hello, ma'am

18:28.200 --> 18:28.880
Auntie Yu

18:29.640 --> 18:30.000
Please sit

18:30.640 --> 18:31.200
Make yourself comfortable

18:32.119 --> 18:32.599
Take a look

18:32.720 --> 18:33.519
Would you like something to drink

18:35.759 --> 18:36.480
No rush

18:36.799 --> 18:37.839
I'm waiting for a friend

18:39.160 --> 18:39.400
Alright

18:40.519 --> 18:41.640
We'll wait for your friend

18:41.680 --> 18:42.440
and order together

18:48.759 --> 18:49.359
Auntie Yu

18:50.240 --> 18:51.119
Jiaqi, over here

18:52.519 --> 18:53.119
Auntie Yu

18:53.200 --> 18:54.640
It's been so long since we met

18:54.839 --> 18:55.440
It really has

18:57.480 --> 18:58.640
You're still so beautiful

18:59.920 --> 19:01.079
Let me introduce you

19:01.279 --> 19:02.440
This is Lin Jiaqi

19:02.519 --> 19:03.559
She works in investment banking

19:03.839 --> 19:04.640
This is Xu Yan

19:04.920 --> 19:05.799
Hao Ming's friend

19:06.839 --> 19:07.279
Hello

19:07.920 --> 19:08.319
Hello

19:08.519 --> 19:09.240
Nice to meet you

19:12.960 --> 19:13.480
Jiaqi

19:14.000 --> 19:15.880
I heard you worked at a Wall Street bank

19:15.960 --> 19:17.200
and did really well

19:17.680 --> 19:18.880
Why did you suddenly come back

19:20.200 --> 19:21.359
It was my father's wish

19:21.640 --> 19:22.440
After so many years

19:22.519 --> 19:23.400
I've finally fulfilled it

19:24.000 --> 19:24.920
And I just got

19:24.960 --> 19:25.720
an offer from Hong Kong

19:25.920 --> 19:26.640
The terms are pretty good

19:26.799 --> 19:27.480
So I came back

19:29.319 --> 19:30.960
The development here is great now

19:31.680 --> 19:32.079
By the way

19:32.279 --> 19:33.640
Our family's Dewei project

19:33.720 --> 19:35.440
was thanks to your help choosing a partner

19:35.480 --> 19:36.640
You're too kind

19:37.160 --> 19:38.200
You and Uncle Shen

19:38.519 --> 19:39.720
both watched me grow up

19:40.880 --> 19:41.799
What have you been busy with lately

19:42.319 --> 19:43.640
I just got back recently

19:43.680 --> 19:44.480
I'm taking a break now

19:51.920 --> 19:52.400
Xu Yan

19:54.400 --> 19:56.359
Yutong is a top young lawyer

19:56.839 --> 19:58.839
specializing in cross-border M&A and investment

19:59.599 --> 20:00.319
Now she's at

20:00.319 --> 20:01.759
her family's law firm

20:02.039 --> 20:03.039
handling international business

20:06.759 --> 20:07.279
Hello

20:08.680 --> 20:09.200
Yutong

20:09.440 --> 20:10.799
I saw your mom a few days ago

20:11.079 --> 20:12.359
She said you just handled

20:12.440 --> 20:13.599
a multinational merger case

20:13.640 --> 20:14.440
and did a great job

20:15.079 --> 20:16.359
Then I'll campaign for myself

20:16.559 --> 20:17.160
Auntie Yu

20:17.240 --> 20:18.279
If your family has international business

20:18.400 --> 20:19.119
remember to call me

20:19.720 --> 20:20.400
Of course

20:20.759 --> 20:22.279
I wouldn't trust anyone else

20:31.960 --> 20:32.680
Miss Xu

20:34.200 --> 20:35.680
What do you think of these girls

20:36.359 --> 20:37.039
They're all great

20:37.559 --> 20:39.000
Each one is talented and beautiful

20:42.799 --> 20:43.359
Yes

20:44.079 --> 20:45.279
Girls like these

20:45.599 --> 20:46.559
are the right match for Hao Ming

20:47.960 --> 20:49.279
I don't like beating around the bush

20:49.319 --> 20:50.480
and wasting each other's time

20:51.960 --> 20:52.960
Although your image

20:53.000 --> 20:54.279
and education are excellent

20:54.680 --> 20:55.559
and your job is good

20:58.039 --> 20:58.920
But

20:59.559 --> 21:01.079
your family background isn't great

21:13.960 --> 21:14.839
Last time we were together

21:14.839 --> 21:16.000
for quite a while

21:16.599 --> 21:18.200
you couldn't fit in at all

21:18.799 --> 21:20.119
but never complained

21:21.519 --> 21:23.079
Even when I asked you to get takeout

21:23.759 --> 21:24.839
you didn't get upset

21:25.519 --> 21:26.279
Even when ignored

21:26.319 --> 21:27.279
you kept smiling

21:29.720 --> 21:30.680
Just like now

21:31.599 --> 21:32.720
still not angry

21:36.519 --> 21:37.200
Miss Xu

21:38.279 --> 21:39.480
Your problem is

21:40.640 --> 21:41.839
you're too good at enduring

21:42.519 --> 21:43.519
As you saw

21:44.160 --> 21:45.799
these girls just now

21:46.720 --> 21:48.200
all have a relaxed attitude

21:48.240 --> 21:48.880
a sense of ease

21:49.440 --> 21:50.839
That's what suits Hao Ming

21:51.519 --> 21:53.240
and exactly what you lack

21:55.960 --> 21:57.039
You're better suited for

21:57.079 --> 21:58.799
someone truly in step with you

22:07.480 --> 22:08.160
Qiao Yan

22:08.400 --> 22:10.079
Orphan, wild child

22:10.240 --> 22:12.519
Orphan, wild child

22:12.640 --> 22:15.319
Orphan, wild child

22:15.480 --> 22:17.799
Orphan, wild child

22:17.880 --> 22:18.799
I'm not

22:19.240 --> 22:20.519
The wild child hit someone

22:20.680 --> 22:22.000
The wild child hit someone

22:22.119 --> 22:23.559
I'm not a wild child

22:24.000 --> 22:25.519
I have parents

22:25.640 --> 22:28.440
My parents are abroad

22:28.519 --> 22:30.680
Far, far away

22:30.759 --> 22:32.039
Qiao Yan, liar

22:32.119 --> 22:34.160
Qiao Yan, liar

22:39.599 --> 22:40.920
Break up with Hao Ming right away.

22:42.039 --> 22:43.200
So you don't embarrass yourself.

22:46.559 --> 22:47.920
Syracuse University

22:51.640 --> 22:53.160
It's the school where my parents

22:53.960 --> 22:54.920
work overseas.

22:56.119 --> 22:57.359
They taught me from a young age

22:58.279 --> 22:59.880
that no matter the situation,

23:00.240 --> 23:01.319
grace and manners

23:02.759 --> 23:03.839
are basic courtesy.

23:07.039 --> 23:07.960
I just didn't expect

23:08.000 --> 23:09.079
that in your eyes,

23:11.559 --> 23:12.759
it's timidity and restraint.

23:14.640 --> 23:15.400
My work here in China

23:15.440 --> 23:16.319
is all my own effort.

23:16.759 --> 23:18.079
I rarely mention my parents.

23:18.759 --> 23:19.960
But to you,

23:22.079 --> 23:23.200
it means a poor family background.

23:26.640 --> 23:27.920
I can only say you're mistaken.

23:29.519 --> 23:30.160
I know

23:31.039 --> 23:32.039
you don't like me.

23:33.079 --> 23:34.000
That's understandable.

23:35.319 --> 23:36.359
But I love Hao Ming

23:39.440 --> 23:40.359
and won't leave him.

25:10.839 --> 25:11.480
What are you thinking about?

25:13.160 --> 25:13.880
Nothing, really.

25:15.279 --> 25:16.240
Just feel this family

25:16.640 --> 25:17.759
is a bit strange somehow.

25:19.359 --> 25:20.079
Strange how?

25:21.000 --> 25:21.759
I can't put my finger on it.

25:25.079 --> 25:25.960
I think they're fine.

25:26.039 --> 25:26.440
Look,

25:26.519 --> 25:28.319
they're a highly educated family.

25:29.400 --> 25:30.839
If we become relatives,

25:30.920 --> 25:33.039
it'll help our company's image

25:33.119 --> 25:34.640
in many ways.

25:36.000 --> 25:36.680
Don't overthink it.

25:36.720 --> 25:37.200
I think

25:37.480 --> 25:38.599
our son has good taste.

25:40.559 --> 25:41.680
Thinking too much.

25:45.000 --> 25:46.440
Maybe I'm just overthinking.

25:59.000 --> 25:59.640
Good morning, everyone.

26:00.720 --> 26:01.440
Good morning, Mr. Shen.

26:03.519 --> 26:04.400
Old Qu isn't here yet?

26:04.759 --> 26:05.759
I haven't had a chance to tell you.

26:06.319 --> 26:07.519
Mr. Qu isn't feeling well today.

26:07.720 --> 26:08.319
He can't make it.

26:09.160 --> 26:09.640
Alright.

26:09.759 --> 26:10.839
Let's not wait for him. Let's start.

26:12.079 --> 26:13.559
About the new district

26:13.759 --> 26:15.079
complex commercial project,

26:15.680 --> 26:16.240
I'm planning

26:16.279 --> 26:17.319
to work with our upstream partner,

26:17.359 --> 26:18.519
Shifeng Group.

26:19.000 --> 26:19.480
They've also

26:19.480 --> 26:20.839
expressed to me

26:20.920 --> 26:22.480
an initial interest in cooperation.

26:24.039 --> 26:24.599
Shifeng

26:25.200 --> 26:26.920
is currently the largest

26:27.440 --> 26:28.680
and most well-funded company.

26:29.640 --> 26:30.720
If we can reach

26:30.759 --> 26:31.680
a partnership with them,

26:32.160 --> 26:32.759
this project

26:33.400 --> 26:33.839
will be secure.

26:33.880 --> 26:35.000
Looks like our chances are good.

26:35.000 --> 26:35.400
Yeah.

26:48.279 --> 26:48.880
Hao Ming

26:50.799 --> 26:51.200
Dad

26:53.119 --> 26:55.319
You didn't speak up in the meeting.

26:55.839 --> 26:56.440
Why?

26:57.680 --> 26:59.480
I'm not optimistic about Shifeng Group.

26:59.720 --> 27:01.119
Their new chairman, Mr. Zheng.

27:01.400 --> 27:02.000
What's your reason?

27:04.559 --> 27:05.160
First,

27:05.759 --> 27:06.720
Shifeng's resettlement housing

27:06.920 --> 27:08.400
had an accident at the construction site.

27:09.640 --> 27:10.599
His decision was

27:11.599 --> 27:12.480
to cover it up

27:12.960 --> 27:13.680
and suppress public opinion.

27:14.039 --> 27:14.920
He lacks responsibility.

27:16.079 --> 27:16.599
Second,

27:16.799 --> 27:17.759
he was parachuted in mid-career,

27:18.480 --> 27:20.359
meaning inside Shifeng

27:20.440 --> 27:22.200
he has no trusted team.

27:23.960 --> 27:24.519
Third,

27:25.200 --> 27:26.359
he brought three close aides.

27:26.640 --> 27:28.079
One is very social

27:28.680 --> 27:29.799
but stubborn and self-centered,

27:30.440 --> 27:31.279
offending people everywhere.

27:32.359 --> 27:33.240
Another one

27:33.599 --> 27:34.799
is older and experienced,

27:35.759 --> 27:37.519
but during the accident

27:37.640 --> 27:39.039
he was playing mahjong in a private room.

27:40.119 --> 27:41.000
The third one,

27:41.400 --> 27:42.599
the lowest ranked,

27:42.640 --> 27:44.039
is the most capable at work.

27:44.680 --> 27:45.680
He handles a lot of tasks.

27:46.279 --> 27:47.920
But long-term benefits are unfairly divided.

27:49.839 --> 27:50.440
Impressive.

27:51.440 --> 27:52.440
You've figured out

27:52.519 --> 27:53.480
their situation so thoroughly.

27:54.200 --> 27:54.559
Dad

27:55.240 --> 27:56.319
I think internally

27:57.680 --> 27:59.000
there will be turmoil.

28:00.079 --> 28:01.519
If you think Mr. Zheng

28:02.200 --> 28:02.559
right,

28:02.839 --> 28:03.960
has so many issues,

28:04.559 --> 28:05.319
then how did he become

28:05.359 --> 28:06.319
the chairman?

28:06.799 --> 28:08.240
That's his bigger risk.

28:10.000 --> 28:10.640
Hao Ming,

28:10.920 --> 28:11.960
in construction,

28:12.880 --> 28:13.599
if you haven't

28:13.640 --> 28:15.440
started from the bottom,

28:16.119 --> 28:17.440
haven't fought in this field,

28:17.720 --> 28:18.640
struggled and competed,

28:18.640 --> 28:20.359
for twenty or thirty years,

28:20.839 --> 28:22.759
you won't even know the ropes.

28:25.200 --> 28:25.839
Understand?

28:27.680 --> 28:28.119
I understand.

28:30.720 --> 28:31.480
Also,

28:31.680 --> 28:32.799
I want to bid

28:33.240 --> 28:33.880
for the new district's

28:33.920 --> 28:34.920
Plot No. 178.

28:40.599 --> 28:42.000
Such a big company like this

28:43.119 --> 28:43.599
sooner or later

28:43.680 --> 28:45.160
will end up in your hands.

28:45.960 --> 28:47.000
Right now,

28:48.240 --> 28:50.359
if you stay steady and avoid mistakes,

28:50.880 --> 28:52.359
that's your biggest achievement.

28:53.319 --> 28:53.960
You understand?

28:56.559 --> 28:57.039
I do.

28:57.720 --> 28:59.519
One meal, a cherished moment.

28:59.720 --> 29:01.039
This episode of Family Feast

29:01.039 --> 29:01.839
ends right here.

29:01.920 --> 29:03.559
Thank you all for watching.

29:03.640 --> 29:03.880
Got it.

29:03.920 --> 29:04.799
See you next time

29:05.039 --> 29:05.559
Goodbye, goodbye.

29:05.839 --> 29:06.400
Cut.

29:11.319 --> 29:12.200
Thanks for your hard work, Siwei.

29:12.359 --> 29:13.319
What a messed-up process.

29:13.359 --> 29:14.240
We've been recording for so long.

29:17.559 --> 29:18.920
Thank you, Teacher Sanmu.

29:19.680 --> 29:20.640
It's really late today.

29:20.680 --> 29:21.640
You worked hard too.

29:21.759 --> 29:22.240
Xu Yan

29:22.640 --> 29:23.200
To be honest,

29:23.960 --> 29:24.880
the reason I came this time

29:25.039 --> 29:27.000
besides Hao Ming,

29:27.559 --> 29:28.079
mainly

29:28.119 --> 29:29.480
I was moved by your sincerity.

29:29.880 --> 29:31.400
I was on a business trip in the US for a week,

29:31.599 --> 29:32.960
and you kept sending me messages.

29:33.200 --> 29:34.519
Whenever I messaged you,

29:34.559 --> 29:35.640
you replied right away.

29:36.920 --> 29:37.839
I'm really curious,

29:38.319 --> 29:39.599
do you ever sleep?

29:40.119 --> 29:41.480
Sorry for bothering you.

29:42.039 --> 29:43.480
That's just how our job is.

29:43.559 --> 29:44.759
We're on call twenty-four hours.

29:44.920 --> 29:45.440
So,

29:45.559 --> 29:46.440
if you have any questions later,

29:46.440 --> 29:47.359
just contact me directly.

29:47.880 --> 29:48.279
Sure.

29:48.519 --> 29:49.039
I have high hopes for you.

29:49.960 --> 29:50.920
Next time you meet Hao Ming,

29:51.000 --> 29:51.799
let's have a meal together.

29:52.000 --> 29:52.599
No problem.

29:53.640 --> 29:54.400
You worked hard today.

29:54.480 --> 29:55.319
Go home and rest early.

29:55.559 --> 29:55.759
Come on.

29:55.799 --> 29:56.119
Alright.

29:56.400 --> 29:57.000
Take Teacher Sanmu

29:57.000 --> 29:57.759
to the guest room to change.

29:59.400 --> 29:59.839
Sister Yan

30:00.079 --> 30:00.759
The director backstage said

30:00.799 --> 30:01.559
those dishes just now

30:01.599 --> 30:02.680
need a few more close-up shots.

30:02.960 --> 30:03.440
No problem.

30:09.640 --> 30:10.680
Hello, Auntie Yu.

30:12.039 --> 30:12.759
Right now?

30:14.079 --> 30:14.680
I still have

30:16.240 --> 30:16.960
No problem.

30:17.759 --> 30:19.160
Please send me the address.

30:20.319 --> 30:20.759
Okay.

30:35.200 --> 30:35.720
Thank you.

30:36.920 --> 30:38.240
I'm coming in now, Auntie Yu.

30:39.640 --> 30:40.039
Alright.

30:45.119 --> 30:45.440
This one here

30:45.440 --> 30:47.160
is our Tongzhou Canal.

30:47.319 --> 30:47.880
And then,

30:48.000 --> 30:49.279
there's the central business district nearby.

30:50.039 --> 30:51.039
Sorry, Auntie Yu,

30:51.640 --> 30:52.960
I was late because of traffic.

30:53.680 --> 30:54.720
We've been waiting for you.

30:56.279 --> 30:57.160
It wasn't easy today

30:57.160 --> 30:57.920
to arrange for President Meng

30:58.079 --> 30:59.319
to join us for house viewing.

30:59.559 --> 31:00.720
And you made others wait so long.

31:01.440 --> 31:01.960
Auntie Meng

31:02.279 --> 31:02.880
Sorry.

31:03.039 --> 31:03.559
It's fine.

31:04.440 --> 31:05.799
Let's hurry and take a look.

31:05.960 --> 31:06.880
I have another appointment this afternoon.

31:06.920 --> 31:07.279
Okay.

31:14.480 --> 31:15.359
The whole development's

31:15.400 --> 31:16.200
land area

31:16.279 --> 31:18.160
is 35,000 square meters.

31:18.519 --> 31:20.480
There are eight buildings in total.

31:20.640 --> 31:22.559
Six are garden houses,

31:22.640 --> 31:23.880
two are high-rises.

31:24.519 --> 31:26.200
The size range is

31:26.200 --> 31:26.960
one hundred ninety-nine

31:27.039 --> 31:28.400
to one hundred forty-three.

31:28.920 --> 31:29.519
Sister Lan

31:29.960 --> 31:30.880
This time, buying a house

31:30.920 --> 31:32.079
is for whom?

31:32.400 --> 31:32.880
My son.

31:33.119 --> 31:33.839
He's getting married.

31:34.400 --> 31:35.279
Really?

31:35.400 --> 31:36.480
Congratulations, Sister Lan.

31:36.640 --> 31:38.480
Young President Shen is getting married so soon.

31:38.759 --> 31:39.799
I wonder which family's daughter

31:39.839 --> 31:40.920
is so lucky.

31:45.000 --> 31:46.559
Look at me, so clueless.

31:47.599 --> 31:48.519
Hello, ma'am.

31:48.880 --> 31:49.599
My name is Lisa.

31:49.839 --> 31:50.799
If you have any requests,

31:50.920 --> 31:51.640
just let me know.

31:51.680 --> 31:52.440
I'll make sure you're satisfied.

31:52.559 --> 31:53.480
Thank you, sorry for the trouble.

31:53.599 --> 31:54.000
It's nothing.

31:54.880 --> 31:55.279
Lisa

31:55.279 --> 31:57.119
Which units did you prepare for me?

31:57.359 --> 31:58.480
The ones I prepared for us

31:58.519 --> 32:00.160
are the best units in the development.

32:00.240 --> 32:02.039
Building 6, unit 606,

32:02.480 --> 32:03.400
706,

32:03.680 --> 32:04.720
and 808.

32:05.480 --> 32:06.359
These three units

32:06.400 --> 32:07.440
are definitely the best

32:07.519 --> 32:08.000
and largest

32:08.119 --> 32:09.079
layouts in the development.

32:09.119 --> 32:10.279
I've reserved all of them for you.

32:10.839 --> 32:11.400
Ma'am,

32:11.839 --> 32:12.960
what do you think?

32:16.640 --> 32:17.319
They're all great.

32:19.160 --> 32:19.759
Auntie Yu,

32:21.519 --> 32:23.000
should we ask Hao Ming's opinion?

32:28.240 --> 32:29.000
Miss Xu

32:29.440 --> 32:31.079
For things like buying a wedding home

32:31.839 --> 32:33.279
Aunt Lan should definitely decide

32:34.480 --> 32:35.200
You young people

32:35.240 --> 32:36.720
don’t really understand houses

32:36.960 --> 32:37.720
Not to mention anything else

32:38.000 --> 32:39.599
just the direction of the house

32:39.640 --> 32:40.640
and the floor, for example

32:40.799 --> 32:42.119
You probably have no idea, right?

32:42.240 --> 32:43.759
In a few years, you’ll want kids

32:44.200 --> 32:45.160
so you need to think carefully

32:45.200 --> 32:46.599
about the house’s layout

32:46.759 --> 32:48.079
and what style to decorate it in

32:48.319 --> 32:49.440
This isn’t a joke

32:49.880 --> 32:51.400
If you choose the wrong house

32:52.039 --> 32:53.119
it’ll affect your married life

32:53.160 --> 32:54.440
in a very big way

32:56.559 --> 32:57.640
Thank you, Auntie Meng

32:58.759 --> 32:59.319
When buying a house

32:59.319 --> 33:00.680
we’ll definitely listen to Auntie Yu

33:02.319 --> 33:03.880
I just meant to say

33:03.920 --> 33:04.519
should we let Hao Ming

33:04.519 --> 33:05.480
come over and take a look together?

33:05.799 --> 33:06.319
No need

33:07.759 --> 33:08.519
He’s so busy

33:09.039 --> 33:10.240
We can decide for him

33:10.920 --> 33:11.359
Okay

33:14.960 --> 33:15.720
I understand

33:16.519 --> 33:18.519
Miss Xu probably doesn’t look at houses often

33:18.640 --> 33:19.519
She doesn’t have much experience

33:20.599 --> 33:21.480
But that’s alright

33:21.920 --> 33:22.759
Auntie Meng is here

33:23.079 --> 33:24.359
I’ll help you two

33:24.400 --> 33:25.400
pick the best house

33:25.799 --> 33:26.240
Thank you

33:27.160 --> 33:28.200
You don’t have to say that

33:28.359 --> 33:29.440
We’re getting older

33:29.920 --> 33:30.519
We really don’t know

33:30.559 --> 33:31.759
what young people are thinking

33:32.680 --> 33:33.359
Xu Yan’s father

33:33.400 --> 33:34.559
studied architecture

33:35.240 --> 33:36.720
She’s been influenced since childhood

33:37.119 --> 33:37.599
So it’s perfect

33:38.000 --> 33:39.720
You can look from a professional view

33:39.960 --> 33:40.960
at these houses

33:41.359 --> 33:42.319
and see which is best

34:22.559 --> 34:23.000
Mom

34:31.800 --> 34:32.360
Son

34:32.760 --> 34:33.599
Why are you here?

34:36.360 --> 34:37.239
Did you tell him?

34:38.880 --> 34:39.639
No, Auntie Yu

34:39.719 --> 34:40.079
I didn’t

34:40.119 --> 34:40.800
No

34:41.400 --> 34:42.400
I asked the driver where you were

34:42.519 --> 34:43.679
He said you were here

34:43.920 --> 34:45.719
So I guessed you were buying me a house

34:46.000 --> 34:46.960
I forgot to tell you

34:47.000 --> 34:48.360
I’ve already picked out the house

34:48.920 --> 34:49.719
When did this happen?

34:49.760 --> 34:50.679
I had no idea

34:51.079 --> 34:52.079
It’s been a while

34:52.639 --> 34:53.800
I didn’t even tell Yan Yan

34:55.480 --> 34:56.599
I wanted to surprise you

34:58.519 --> 34:59.119
This kid

34:59.400 --> 35:00.440
But the houses here are nice

35:00.840 --> 35:01.880
If there’s nothing else

35:02.320 --> 35:02.960
I’ll go with my girlfriend

35:02.960 --> 35:03.599
on our date now

35:05.199 --> 35:05.599
Bye

35:06.679 --> 35:07.280
Bye, Auntie Meng

35:07.360 --> 35:07.760
Alright

35:07.840 --> 35:09.159
I spent a long time choosing this house

35:09.480 --> 35:09.880
Lisa

35:11.239 --> 35:11.960
Sorry about that

35:13.000 --> 35:13.559
Okay, okay

35:13.760 --> 35:14.360
Take your time looking

35:14.400 --> 35:14.760
Bye

35:16.360 --> 35:17.599
We’ll head out now, Auntie Yu

35:17.639 --> 35:18.239
Thank you

35:18.840 --> 35:19.719
Goodbye, Auntie Meng

35:48.239 --> 35:49.639
I keep forgetting to ask you

35:50.639 --> 35:51.079
why

35:51.119 --> 35:52.239
you like agave so much

35:54.199 --> 35:56.360
Agave only blooms once in its life

35:59.960 --> 36:01.599
after growing for decades

36:02.039 --> 36:03.280
using all its strength

36:03.599 --> 36:04.599
to create a cloud of flowers

36:09.119 --> 36:09.920
I really love

36:09.960 --> 36:11.039
its tenacious vitality

36:12.199 --> 36:12.679
And also

36:13.440 --> 36:14.239
how it stores up energy

36:15.079 --> 36:15.960
inside itself

36:16.199 --> 36:17.639
waiting for that one burst in a lifetime

36:19.119 --> 36:20.039
It’s a species that’s existed

36:20.079 --> 36:21.079
for hundreds of millions of years

36:22.199 --> 36:23.239
That kind of vitality

36:24.119 --> 36:25.519
is unique among plants

36:26.400 --> 36:26.960
Yan Yan

36:28.079 --> 36:28.679
Come try

36:29.079 --> 36:29.880
the Mexican wraps I made

36:34.000 --> 36:34.719
They’re ready

36:36.679 --> 36:37.760
They come from the same place

36:38.199 --> 36:39.480
as agave

36:42.119 --> 36:42.760
Is it good?

36:46.400 --> 36:47.559
You’re a great cook

36:50.000 --> 36:50.920
This is for you

36:54.320 --> 36:54.840
Why

36:54.840 --> 36:55.840
are you suddenly giving me a gift?

36:57.599 --> 36:59.119
You’ve worked hard accompanying my mom lately

37:00.800 --> 37:01.840
I’ll tell her

37:02.480 --> 37:03.480
not to take up

37:03.920 --> 37:04.840
too much of your time

37:05.880 --> 37:06.599
Every time Auntie

37:06.639 --> 37:08.199
always schedules with me in advance

37:08.360 --> 37:09.920
She never delays anything for me

37:09.960 --> 37:10.599
Don’t worry

37:11.480 --> 37:13.239
Your planner is packed

37:13.360 --> 37:14.639
with my mom’s schedule

37:15.519 --> 37:16.280
But you’ve never

37:16.320 --> 37:17.559
complained to me once

37:19.320 --> 37:20.199
So what’s this?

37:21.519 --> 37:22.679
A reward for a good student

37:24.239 --> 37:24.760
Yan Yan

37:25.840 --> 37:26.480
Your kindness

37:27.280 --> 37:28.840
makes me want to give you

37:29.480 --> 37:30.239
all the good things I see

37:42.320 --> 37:43.159
I heard you’re applying

37:43.199 --> 37:44.360
to be the hostess of Family Feast, right?

37:47.760 --> 37:48.639
How did you know?

37:50.280 --> 37:51.119
I also know

37:51.280 --> 37:52.639
the current hostess

37:52.880 --> 37:54.320
is a bit overbearing

37:54.559 --> 37:55.800
and especially loves to complain to her mom

37:57.079 --> 37:57.840
Don’t worry

37:59.159 --> 37:59.719
about these things

38:00.280 --> 38:01.519
I can help you handle them

38:06.480 --> 38:07.800
Thank you for your kindness

38:08.599 --> 38:09.679
But I don’t need you to help me like that

38:11.000 --> 38:12.280
She has her family’s support

38:13.039 --> 38:13.599
And so do you

38:25.760 --> 38:26.320
Hao Ming

38:29.119 --> 38:29.960
You made me realize

38:30.000 --> 38:31.599
the best man in the world.

38:34.679 --> 38:35.559
Thank you for loving me.

38:38.760 --> 38:40.199
But when it comes to work,

38:42.079 --> 38:42.960
you have to trust me.

38:43.920 --> 38:44.719
I can handle it.

38:46.840 --> 38:47.280
Okay.

38:48.559 --> 38:49.239
I trust you.

38:51.119 --> 38:52.079
Eat quickly, it's getting cold.

38:53.440 --> 38:53.920
One more.

38:54.760 --> 38:55.360
Have another.

38:56.119 --> 38:56.760
Alright, come here.

38:57.039 --> 38:57.559
I'll show you.

38:59.599 --> 39:00.039
Come.

39:05.199 --> 39:07.280
Every time Hao Ming confesses sincerely,

39:07.679 --> 39:08.840
every time he supports me,

39:09.559 --> 39:11.159
it's as if he's always asking me,

39:12.199 --> 39:13.719
Do you deserve pure love?
